@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=UnifrakturCook:700');

Well apparently userstyles.org doesn't allow non-chrome imports so Fraktur won't apply unless you change it manually. If you want to do so, copy and paste the paragraph below instead of other font-family property and its value. Then just uncomment here, delete this and the paragraph below.

font-family: 'UnifrakturCook', cursive !important;
*/

